0fact%20that%20the%20watch's%20features%20can%20fit%20into%20a%20wearable%2045mm%20case%20without%20compromising%20the%20thickness%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20testament%20to%20Vacheron%20Constantin's%20mastery%20of%20miniaturization%20and%20innovation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20number%20of%20complications%20might%20make%20it%20less%20practical%20for%20everyday%20wear%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20Solaria%20will%20captivate%20serious%20collectors%20and%20enthusiasts%20of%20haute%20horology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacheron-constantin-unveiled-an-complicated-wrist-watch-41-complications-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743573986000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ecb0ed69253ccddf9af856%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacheron-constantin-unveiled-an-complicated-wrist-watch-41-complications-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20timepiece%20comprises%20over%201%2C500%20components%20and%20has%2041%20functions%20besides%20telling%20time%2C%20such%20as%20locating%20the%20position%20of%20the%20stars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacheron-constantin-unveiled-an-complicated-wrist-watch-41-complications-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haldiram%20Sells%20Stake%20To%20International%20Holding%20Company%2C%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHaldiram%20Snacks%20Food%2C%20the%20country's%20leading%20snack%20and%20food%20brand%2C%20on%20Monday%20confirmed%20selling%20its%20stake%20to%20two%20new%20investors%20--%20IHC%20(International%20Holding%20Company)%20and%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global%20--%20according%20to%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20statement%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Haldiram%20confirmed%20acquisition%20of%20a%20minority%20stake%20by%20Singapore-based%20global%20investment%20firm%20Temasek.%20The%20details%20of%20this%20deal%20were%20also%20not%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaldirams%2C%20India's%20leading%20snack%20and%20food%20brand%2C%20is%20pleased%20to%20announce%20the%20addition%20of%20two%20new%20investors%2C%20IHC%20(International%20Holding%20Company)%20and%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global%2C%20to%20its%20ongoing%20equity%20round%2C%20following%20Temasek's%20recent%20participation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategic%20move%20further%20strengthens%20Haldirams%20financial%20position%20as%20it%20accelerates%20its%20global%20expansion%20plans%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investment%20reflects%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global's%20and%20IHC's%20commitment%20to%20backing%20dominant%20companies%20with%20strong%20consumer%20brands%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20industry%20sources%2C%20IHC%20and%20Alpha%20Wave%20are%20collectively%20acquiring%20a%20minority%20stake%20of%20about%206%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Haldiram%20Snacks%20Food%20at%20a%20valuation%20of%20USD%2010%20billion%20(around%20Rs%2085%2C000%20crore)%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20for%20the%20Indian%20packaged%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlpha%20Wave%20is%20a%20global%20investment%20company%20that%20focuses%20on%20three%20main%20verticals%20--%20private%20equity%2C%20private%20credit%2C%20and%20public%20markets%20--%20while%20UAE-based%20IHC%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20investment%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20backing%20of%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global%20and%20IHC%2C%20Haldirams%20is%20set%20to%20leverage%20the%20vast%20expertise%20and%20networks%20of%20these%20investors%20to%20broaden%20its%20footprint%20in%20key%20international%20markets%20such%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Middle%20East%2C%20while%20strengthening%20its%20footprint%20and%20presence%20further%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20markets%2C%20which%20demonstrate%20growing%20demand%20for%20Indian%20cuisine%20and%20snacks%2C%20will%20be%20the%20primary%20focus%20areas%20in%20the%20company's%20global%20expansion%20strategy%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20development%2C%20Haldirams%20group's%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20partnership%20represents%20patient%20capital%20and%20long-term%20support%20to%20Haldirams'%20growth%20plans.%20With%20this%20partnership%2C%20we%20are%20well-positioned%20to%20enhance%20our%20product%20offerings%2C%20expand%20our%20operations%2C%20and%20further%20our%20mission%20to%20make%20Haldirams%20a%20household%20name%20in%20Middle%20East%20and%20other%20international%20geographies.%26quot%3B%20Rick%20Gerson%2C%20Co-founder%20and%20Chairman%20of%20Alpha%20Wave%20Global%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20proud%20to%20become%20a%20shareholder%20and%20partner%20with%20Haldirams%20in%20this%20next%20stage%20of%20their%20growth%20both%20domestic%20and%20internationally%3B%20while%20maintaining%20the%20delight%20they%20have%20brought%20to%20customers%20for%20close%20to%20century.%26quot%3B%20IHC%20CEO%20Syed%20Basar%20Shueb%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20investment%20aligns%20with%20Alpha%20Wave's%20and%20IHC's%20strategy%20to%20support%20leading%20companies%20that%20are%20making%20a%20global%20impact.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20Haldirams%20to%20drive%20innovation%20and%20expand%20its%20market%20presence.%26quot%3B%20PwC%20Investment%20Banking%20team%20acted%20as%20advisor%20to%20the%20transaction%20and%20Kha