-india-white-house-125040200332_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20confirmed%20that%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20will%20be%20effective%20immediately%20after%20Trump's%20announcement.%20However%2C%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20auto%20imports%20will%20be%20effective%20from%20April%203%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fdonald-trump-reciprocal-tariffs-date-time-india-white-house-125040200332_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20Tariffs%20May%20Impact%20India%20And%20The%20Silver%20Lining%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20unleash%20his%20sweeping%20global%20tariffs%20today%20amid%20fears%20that%20equity%20markets%20could%20go%20on%20a%20whirlwind%20and%20force%20countries%20to%20take%20emergency%20measures.%20It%20will%20most%20likely%20result%20in%20an%20all-out%20trade%20war.%20Gripped%20by%20a%20stark%20frenzy%2C%20the%20world%20could%20see%20an%20economic%20meltdown%20due%20to%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20suggesting%20that%20this%20could%20essentially%20be%20the%20third%20world%20war%20that%20many%20anticipated%20would%20arise%20from%20the%20conflicts%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20or%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20billed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20stop%20the%20US%20industries%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bripped%20off%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20trading%20nations.%20He%20has%20appeared%20to%20expand%20his%20tariff%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Ball%20countries%26quot%3B%20but%20kept%20the%20world%20guessing%20about%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20repeated%20remarks%20on%20India%20being%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20tariffing%20nations%26quot%3B%20suggest%20New%20Delhi%20must%20brace%20for%20heavy%20impact%20as%20the%20mega%20trade%20plan%20rolls%20out%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20India%20May%20Be%20Hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20tariffs%20could%20significantly%20impact%20Indian%20exports%2C%20think%20tank%20Global%20Trade%20Research%20Initiative%20(GTRI)%20has%20warned.%20A%20uniform%20tariff%20could%20leave%20India%20facing%20an%20additional%20tax%20of%204.9%25%20compared%20to%20the%20current%202.8%25%2C%20impacting%20sectors%20like%20agriculture%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20according%20to%20the%20GTRI's%20%26quot%3BReciprocal%20Tariffs%20and%20India%26quot%3B%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20US%20imposes%20a%20single%20tariff%20on%20all%20products%20from%20India%2C%20it%20would%20be%20an%20additional%204.9%25.%20Currently%2C%20US%20goods%20face%20a%20weighted%20average%20tariff%20of%207.7%25%20in%20India%2C%20while%20Indian%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20face%20only%202.8%25%2C%20leading%20to%20a%204.9%25%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20US%20implements%20separate%20tariffs%2C%20the%20impact%20will%20be%20sector-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20tariffs%20would%20pose%20the%20biggest%20risk%20to%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20-%20tariffs%20on%20shrimp%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20processed%20food%20could%20go%20up%20to%2028.2%25%2C%20and%20pharma%20and%20jewellery%20industries%20by%20over%2010%25.%20The%20electronics%20industry%20could%20face%20up%20to%207.2%25%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESectors%20like%20petroleum%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20garments%20may%20be%20the%20least%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20highlighted%20that%20India's%20tariffs%20remain%20consistent%20with%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20that%20allowed%20the%20developing%20nations%20to%20retain%20higher%20tariffs%20in%20exchange%20for%20trade%20regulations%20that%20favoured%20wealthy%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India's%20next%20move%20is%20not%20yet%20known%2C%20GTRI%20has%20listed%20the%20steps%20that%20a%20country%20facing%20high%20tariffs%20could%20resort%20to%20-%20an%20advance%20tariff%20order%20that%20adopts%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero-for-zero%26quot%3B%20strategy%20and%20subsides%20any%20hard%20impact%2C%20retaliatory%20measures%20like%20China's%2C%20address%20the%20trade%20date%20mismatches%2C%20or%20correct%20exaggerated%20claims%20of%20inflated%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20excellent%20camaraderie%20-%20which%20often%20featured%20in%20the%20two%20leader's%20remarks%20about%20each%20other%20-%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20warding%20off%20any%20heavy%20damage%20-%20unlike%20in%20the%20Chinese%20case%20where%20mutual%20animosity%20has%20worsened%20any%20chance%20of%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Silver%20Lining%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClouds%20come%20with%20a%20silver%20lining%2C%20and%20so%20do%20Trump's%20tariffs.%20Experts%20remain%20optimistic%20that%20additional%20duties%20on%20US%20imports%20from%20countries%20like%20Canada%20would%20make%20them%20less%20competitive%2C%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20Indian%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20GTRI%20founder%20Ajay%20Founder%2C%20the%20US%20tariffs%20threatened%20to%20turn%20Canadian%20products%20more%20competitive%20allowing%20Indian%20companies%20to%20source%20such%20products%20from%20Canada%20at%20lower%20costs.%20This%20came%20with%20two%20benefits%3A%20strengthened%20trade%20ties%20and%20a%20cut%20in%20dependence%20on%20other%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20imposed%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%2C%20China%20and%20Mexico%20after%20his%20takeover%2C%20exporters%20had%20talked%20of%20similar%20opportunities%20for%20Indian%20sellers.%20Federal%20of%20Indian%20Export%20Organisations%20director%20general%20Ajay%20Sahai%20had%20listed%20sectors%20lik