s%20to%20that.%20Because%20you%20are%20disappointing%20the%20Lucknow%20fans%20as%20well.%20They've%20come%20up%20with%20so%20many%20expectations%20of%20winning%20the%20first%20home%20game%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20team%2C%20we%20are%20confident.%20We%20accept%20that%20we've%20lost%20the%20game%2C%20and%20we%20have%20got%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20make%20that%20impact%20in%20the%20home%20leg.%20We%20still%20have%20six%20more%20games%20to%20go%20here%2C%20and%20this%20team%20has%20shown%20in%20the%20season%20so%20far%2C%20whatever%20little%20cricket%20is%20played%2C%20that%20we%20have%20the%20right%20outlook%20and%20the%20mindset%20to%20look%20at%20the%20IPL.%20What%20you%20can%20expect%20is%20innovation%2C%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%2C%20the%20fight%2C%20the%20hunger%2C%20and%20that%20sums%20us%20up%20as%20a%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20injuries%20limiting%20their%20fast-bowling%20options%2C%20LSG%20might%20have%20preferred%20a%20pitch%20that%20favoured%20spin%20or%20at%20least%20neutralized%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20pace%20attack.%20However%2C%20they%20fielded%20only%20two%20frontline%20quicks%2C%20including%20a%20last-minute%20addition%20in%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20while%20their%20squad%20has%20just%20one%20overseas%20fast%20bowler--Shamar%20Joseph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPBKS%20capitalized%20on%20the%20conditions%20with%20their%20pace%20trio%20of%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Lockie%20Ferguson%2C%20and%20Marco%20Jansen%2C%20who%20combined%20for%20figures%20of%205%2F112%20in%2013%20overs%2C%20with%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20chipping%20in%20with%20two%20more%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaheer%2C%20on%20misreading%20the%20pitch%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20are%20saying.%20We%20will%20go%20according%20to%20what%20the%20curator%20tells%20us.%20We%20are%20not%20using%20this%20as%20an%20excuse.%20We%20have%20seen%20during%20the%20last%20season%20that%20it's%20not%20like%20batters%20don't%20have%20to%20struggle%20here%20at%20times.%20All%20these%20things%20go%20on%20in%20cricket.%20But%20the%20way%20the%20home%20team%20should%20get%20support%2C%20everyone%20needs%20to%20know%20this%20is%20our%20home%20team%20that%20is%20playing%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20what%20can%20we%20do%20to%20help%20them%20win%3F%20Everyone's%20contribution%20is%20important.%20We%20will%20find%20a%20way%20to%20win%20matches...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20LSG%20captain%20Rishabh%20Pant%20admitted%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20that%20they%20were%20expecting%20a%20slower%20track%2C%20which%20led%20to%20their%20decision%20to%20replace%20seamer%20Prince%20Yadav%20with%20spinner%20M%20Siddharth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20was%20to%20get%20a%20slower%20wicket.%20We%20felt%20it%20was%20a%20home%20game%3B%20it%20was%20going%20to%20stop%20a%20little%20bit.%20I%20think%20the%20slower%20ones%2C%20when%20bowled%20into%20the%20wicket%2C%20were%20still%20sticking%20in%2C%20but%20we%20weren't%20good%20enough%20on%20the%20day.%20We%20have%20to%20learn%20and%20move%20forward.%20It%20is%20our%20first%20home%20game.%20Still%20assessing%20the%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Pant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELSG%20now%20joins%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20and%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20in%20expressing%20concerns%20over%20home%20pitch%20conditions.%20KKR%20previously%20stated%20they%20wanted%20more%20spin-friendly%20surfaces%20but%20had%20no%20control%20over%20preparations%2C%20while%20CSK--boasting%20the%20best%20home%20win-loss%20record%20in%20IPL%20history--have%20struggled%20to%20predict%20conditions%20at%20their%20ground%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743565140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2