125040200122_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Markets%20Wait%20In%20Fear%20For%20Trump's%20'Liberation%20Day'%20Tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMarkets%20worldwide%20fluctuated%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20investors%20braced%20for%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sweeping%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcements%2C%20hoping%20they%20would%20free%20businesses%20from%20the%20trade-policy%20uncertainty%20that%20has%20weighed%20on%20markets%20for%20weeks.%20President%20Trump%20is%20set%20to%20unveil%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%2C%20aligning%20US%20duties%20with%20those%20of%20other%20nations%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20at%20an%20event%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Rose%20Garden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20commander-in-chief%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20levies%20will%20include%20all%20countries%2C%20but%20specific%20details%20were%20scant.%20He%20has%20already%20imposed%20a%20range%20of%20import%20levies%20on%20China%2C%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20and%20is%20poised%20to%20introduce%20auto%20tariffs%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20White%20House%20aides%20have%20drafted%20a%20proposal%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20of%20around%2020%20per%20cent%20on%20most%20imports%20to%20the%20United%20States.%20White%20House%20spokeswoman%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20impose%20duties%20on%20US%20goods%20would%20take%20effect%20immediately%20after%20Trump%20announces%20them%2C%20while%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20auto%20imports%20will%20take%20effect%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarkets%20Fluctuate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20stocks%20remained%20volatile%20ahead%20of%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20so-called%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20the%20Republican%20billionaire%20said%20were%20required%20to%20combat%20unfair%20trade%20imbalances%20with%20countries%20that%20target%20the%20United%20States.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20shares%20edged%20higher%20in%20choppy%20trading%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20while%20safe-haven%20gold%20soared%20to%20a%20record%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wall%20Street%2C%20the%20benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20ended%20higher%20after%20losing%20ground%20earlier%20in%20the%20session%2C%20with%20gains%20in%20consumer%20discretionary%20communication%20services%2C%20consumer%20staples%20and%20technology%20stocks%20offset%20by%20losses%20in%20healthcare%20and%20financial%20equities.%20The%20Dow%20finished%20a%20shade%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20the%20upcoming%20tariff%20announcement%2C%20we%20still%20don't%20know%20which%20countries%20they'll%20be%20imposed%20on%20and%20what%20rate.%20It's%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20administration%20might%20not%20have%20the%20final%20plan%20ready%20as%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Deutsche%20Bank%20strategist%20Jim%20Reid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20fell%200.03%20per%20cent%20to%2041%2C989.96%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rose%200.38%20per%20cent%20to%205%2C633.07%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20rose%200.87%20per%20cent%20to%2017%2C449.89.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20stocks%20also%20rallied%2C%20recovering%20from%20the%20previous%20day's%20bout%20of%20profit-taking%2C%20particularly%20in%20assets%20that%20are%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20US%20tariffs.%20The%20benchmark%20pan-European%20STOXX%20600%20index%2C%20which%20rose%205.1%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20ended%20up%201%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20technology%2C%20industrial%20and%20financial%20stocks%20leading%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsian%20stocks%20also%20fell%20in%20early%20trading%2C%20after%20a%20choppy%20US%20session.%20Japan's%20Nikkei%20slipped%200.3%20per%20cent%20and%20South%20Korea's%20benchmark%20index%20was%200.57%20per%20cent%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20stocks%20opened%20slightly%20mixed%2C%20with%20the%20blue-chip%20index%20up%200.14%20per%20cent.%20Hong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20was%200.3%20per%20cent%20lower%20in%20early%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20market%20continued%20its%20downward%20move%20for%20another%20session%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20the%20Nifty%2050%20sinking%201.5%20per%20cent.%20The%20reports%20suggest%20further%20weakness.%20Uncertainty%20is%20running%20high%2C%20and%20various%20measures%20of%20stock%2C%20bond%20and%20currency%20volatility%20have%20risen%20sharply%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20reflecting%20the%20challenge%20for%20investors%20of%20trading%20the%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGold%20Eases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20eased%20after%20hitting%20a%20new%20record%20high%20for%20a%20fourth%20straight%20session%2C%20hitting%20%243%2C148.88%20per%20ounce.%20It%20fell%200.15%20per%20cent%20to%20%243%2C118.25%20an%20ounce%2C%20while%20US%20gold%20futures%20settled%200.1%20per%20cent%20lower%20at%20%243%2C146.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20Malek%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20SiebertNXT%2C%20said%20investors%20are%20not%20just%20faced%20with%20uncertainty%20from%20tariffs%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20worried%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20looming%20economic%20slowdown%20given%20weakness%20in%20recent%20data.%20Data%20from%20the%20Institute%20for%20Supply%20Management%20showed%20US%20manufacturing%20contracted%20in%20March%20after%20growing%20for%20two%20straight%20months.%20A%20separate%20report%20from%20the%20Labor%20Department%20showed%20US%20job%20openings%20fell%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20tell%20you%20anecdotally%20that%20the%20number%20of%20client%20calls%20that%20we've%20been%20taking%20lately%20has%20increased%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20about%20tariffs%20but%20they%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Malek%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20losing%20confidence%2C%20and%20that's%20investor%20confidence%2C%20which%20is%20a%20tough%20thing%20to%20fight.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDollar%20Under%20Pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20Treasuries%20sent%20yields%20lower%2C%20with%20benchmark%2010-year%20note%20yields%20falling%208%20basis%20points%20to%204.165%20per%20cent.%20In%20Europe%2C%20the%20yield%20on%20benchmark%20German%2010-year%20Bunds%20fell%200.3%20basis%20points%20to%202.679%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestor%20caution%20toward%20US%20assets%20has%20resulted%20in%20continued%20pressure%20on%20the%20dollar%2C%20which%20posted%20its%20worst%20first-quarter%20performance%20against%20a%20basket%20of%20currencies%20in%20nine%20years%20this%20year%2C%20with%20a%20drop%20of%20nearly%204%20per%20cent.%20The%20Japanese%20yen%20held%20firm%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Swiss%20franc%2C%20as%20traditional%20safe-haven%20assets%20drew%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yen%20strengthened%200.25%20per%20cent%20against%20the%20greenback%20to%20149.57%20per%20dollar.%20Against%20the%20Swiss%20franc%2C%20the%20dollar%20weakened%200.07%20per%20cent%20to%200.884%20franc.%20The%20euro%20was%20down%200.25%20per%20cent%20at%20%241.079.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20index%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20greenback%20against%20a%20basket%20of%20currencies%20including%20the%20yen%20and%20the%20euro%2C%20rose%200.04%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20dollar%20strengthened%200.48%20per%20cent%20versus%20the%20greenback%20to%20%240.6276.%20The%20RBA%20held%20rates%20at%204.1%20per%20cent%2C%20having%20just%20cut%20them%20by%20a%20quarter-point%20in%20February%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20four%20years.%20Bitcoin%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20gained%203.15%20per%20cent%20to%20%2485%2C033.03.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOil%20On%20Edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20edged%20lower%20as%20traders%20weighed%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20from%20Trump%20and%20his%20threats%20to%20impose%20secondary%20tariffs%20on%20Russian%20crude%20and%20attack%20Iran.%20Brent%20futures%20settled%200.37%20per%20cent%20lower%20at%20%2474.49%20a%20barrel.%20US%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20futures%20fell%200.39%20per%20cent%20to%20%2471.20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20To%20Jointly%20Respond%20To%20US%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20have%20agreed%20to%20jointly%20respond%20to%20the%20US%20tariffs%20during%20their%20first%20economic%20discussions%20in%20five%20years%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20countries%20agreed%20that%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20will%20import%20semiconductor%20raw%20materials%20from%20China%2C%20while%20China%20wants%20to%20procure%20chip%20products%20from%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20for%20weeks%20trumpeted%20April%202%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20see%20dramatic%20new%20duties%20that%20could%20upend%20the%20global%20trade%20system.%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20told%20Republican%20House%20lawmakers%20that%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20Trump%20will%20announce%20represent%20a%20%26quot%3Bcap%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20highest%20US%20tariff%20level%20that%20countries%20will%20face%20and%20could%20go%20down%20if%20they%20meet%20the%20administration's%20demands%2C%20according%20to%20Republican%20Representative%20Kevin%20Hern%20from%20Oklahoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20already%20imposed%20tariffs%20on%20aluminum%20and%20steel%20imports%20and%20has%20increased%20duties%20on%20all%20goods%20from%20China.%20But%20he%20has%20also%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20impose%20other%20tariffs%2C%20only%20to%20cancel%20or%20postpone%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743563640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F0eaaeu38_global-market_625x300_02_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-markets-wait-in-fear-for-trumps-liberation-day-tariffs-8066147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Markets%20worldwide%20fluctuated%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20investors%20braced%20for%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sweeping%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcements%2C%20hoping%20they%20would%20free%20businesses%20from%20the%20trade-policy%20uncertainty%20that%20has%20weighed%20on%20markets%20for%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-markets-wait-in-fear-for-trumps-liberation-day-tariffs-8066147%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Billionaire%20Reveals%20Why%20He%20Refused%20To%20Hire%20His%20Own%20Son%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20Not...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprising%20move%2C%20billionaire%20Jorge%20Perez%20denied%20his%20son%20Jon%20Paul%20a%20job%20at%20their%20family's%20real%20estate%20company%2C%20Related%20Group%2C%20until%20he%20gained%20experience%20working%20elsewhere.%C2%A0After%20completing%20college%2C%20Mr%20Perez%20eagerly%20approached%20his%20father%20about%20joining%20the%20family%20business.%20However%2C%20his%20father's%20unexpected%20response%20left%20him%20surprised%20and%20determined%20to%20prove%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20work%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Perez%20recalled%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F03%2F27%2Fbillionaire-jorge-prez-passing-down-the-family-business.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC's%20Inside%20Wealth%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20risk%20his%20reputation%20managing%20their%20%2460%20billion%20asset%20by%20hiring%20his%20son%2C%20just%20because%20they're%20related.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20took%20an%20unconventional%20approach%2C%20sending%20Jon%20Paul%20to%20work%20for%20a%20close%20friend%20and%20business%20partner%20to%20prove%20his%20abilities.%C2%A0As%20a%20result%2C%20Jon%20Paul%20Perez%20reluctantly%20headed%20to%20New%20York%20to%20forge%20his%20path%20after%C2%A0graduating%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Miami.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Perez%20told%20all%20of%20his%20children%20that%20to%20one%20day%20work%20for%20him%2C%20they%20had%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20five%20years%20working%20in%20the%20tough%20New%20York%20real%20estate%20market%20and%20get%20a%20master's%20degree%20from%20a%C2%A0top%20business%20school%C2%A0first.%C2%A0He%20had%20a%20strict%20policy%20to%20ensure%C2%A0his%20children%20weren't%20just%20following%20his%20career%20path%20only%20because%20of%20how%20lucrative%20it%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%2C%20just%20because%20I've%20been%20successful%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20don't%20pick%20something%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20passion%20for.%20Because%20life%20is%20very%20tough%20the%20way%20it%20is%20and%20if%20you%20wake%20up%20every%20day%20and%20do%20something%20just%20for%20making%20money%20or%20that%20you%20don't%20like%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20work.%20I%C2%A0didn't%20want%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20company%20to%20feel%20that%20they%20were%20brought%20in%20because%20of%20their%20last%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Perez%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20son%20began%20his%20career%20as%20an%20analyst%20at%20Related%20Companies%2C%20a%20firm%20owned%20by%20billionaire%20Stephen%20Ross%2C%20a%20close%20family%20friend%20and%20former%20minority%20stakeholder%20in%20Jorge%20Perez's%20company.%20He%20then%20pursued%20further%20education%2C%20earning%20an%20MBA%20from%20Northwestern%20University's%20prestigious%20Kellogg%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20ranked%20the%20No.%203%20business%20school%20in%20the%20country%20by%20Fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202012%2C%20he%20had%20gained%20enough%20experience%20to%20join%20Related%20Group%2C%20but%20his%20father%20didn't%20hand%20him%20a%20top%20role.%20Instead%2C%20Jon%20Paul%20started%20leading%20the%20rental%20business%20and%20worked%20his%20way%20up.%20Years%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20determination%20have%20finally%20paid%20off%20as%20Jon%20Paul%20is%20now%20taking%20the%20reins%20as%20CEO%20of%20Related%20Group%2C%20alongside%20his%20brother%20Nick%2C%20while%20their%20father%20becomes%20executive%20chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20have%20earned%20their%20positions%20in%20the%20company%2C%20having%20worked%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20in%20responsible%20positions%20both%20outside%20and%20inside%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Perez%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bizjournals.com%2Fsouthflorida%2Fnews%2F2025%2F03%2F25%2Frelated-groups-jon-paul-perez-promoted-to-ceo.html%5C%22%3EThe%20South%20Florida%20Business%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743563520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F2s659epg_jorge-perez-_625x300_02_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-billionaire-reveals-why-he-refused-to-hire-his-son-made-him-work-at-a-different-company-8066281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20told%20all%20of%20his%20children%20that%20to%20one%20day%20work%20for%20him%2C%20they%20had%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20five%20years%20working%20in%20the%20tough%20New%20York%20real%20estate%20market%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-billionaire-reveals-why-he-refused-to-hire-his-son-made-him-work-at-a-different-company-8066281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20practises%2