enate%20speech%20-%20from%20the%20possibility%20of%20annexing%20Greenland%20and%20Canada%20to%20slashing%20social%20programs%20and%20cutting%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBooker's%20speech%2C%20occasionally%20interrupted%20by%20Democratic%20colleagues%20to%20whom%20he%20yielded%20for%20questions%20while%20catching%20his%20breath%2C%20came%20as%20Democrats%20are%20in%20the%20minority%20in%20the%20Senate%20and%20the%20House.%20It's%20unclear%20what%20effect%20Booker's%20speech%20could%20have%2C%20but%20it%20reflects%20one%20of%20the%20levers%20available%20to%20out-of-power%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20who%20Booker%20is%20and%20what%20he's%20been%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Booker%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBooker%2C%2055%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20and%20moved%20to%20northern%20New%20Jersey%20when%20he%20was%20a%20boy.%20He's%20spoken%20about%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20Black%20family%20in%20a%20predominantly%20white%20neighborhood%20and%20how%20his%20parents%20faced%20opposition%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20buy%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20played%20football%20in%20college%20at%20Stanford%20University%20before%20attending%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20then%20worked%20as%20an%20attorney%20in%20nonprofits%2C%20giving%20legal%20aid%20to%20poorer%20families.%20Elected%20to%20the%20Newark%20City%20Council%20and%20then%20as%20mayor%20of%20the%20state's%20biggest%20city%2C%20he%20served%20there%20until%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20time%20in%20office%20coincided%20with%20Facebook%20founder%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20%24100%20million%20donation%20to%20the%20city's%20public%20schools%2C%20a%20boon%20that%20burnished%20his%20status%20as%20a%20Democratic%20rising%20star%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20in%20a%20special%20election%20to%20the%20U.S.%20Senate%20after%20the%20death%20of%20incumbent%20Frank%20Lautenberg.%20He%20then%20won%20his%20first%20full-term%20in%202014%20and%20was%20reelected%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20launched%20an%20upbeat%20but%20ultimately%20doomed%202020%20bid%20for%20president%20in%20a%20crowded%20Democratic%20field.%20Standing%20in%20the%20front%20yard%20of%20his%20Newark%20house%2C%20Booker%20declared%20%26quot%3Blove%20ain't%20easy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20He%20Talking%20About%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBooker's%20Senate%20speech%20started%20about%207%20p.m.%20Monday%20and%20carried%20through%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20his%20voice%20occasionally%20wavered%20with%20emotion%20as%20he%20recognized%20his%20colleagues%20who%20asked%20him%20questions%2C%20giving%20him%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20speaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20read%20letters%20from%20constituents%2C%20cited%20authors%20like%20Langston%20Hughes%20and%20leaned%20into%20foreign%20policy%20and%20potential%20social%20safety%20net%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Republicans'%20budget%20language%20aimed%20to%20cut%20health%20care%20for%20Americans%20%26quot%3Bto%20give%20tax%20cuts%20disproportionately%20to%20the%20wealthy%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20drive%20up%20deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20U.S.%20was%20giving%20up%20leading%20the%20planet%20and%20cited%20Trump's%20proposals%20to%20take%20over%20Greenland%20and%20Canada%20while%20feuding%20with%20longtime%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20his%20inclination%20toward%20uplifting%20rhetoric%2C%20Booker%20lamented%20a%20lack%20of%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20union%20in%20trouble%20compared%20to%20our%20global%20peers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYet%20we%20are%20a%20nation%20of%20utter%20abundance%2C%20and%20we've%20proven%20in%20the%20past%20to%20be%20a%20nation%20of%20incredible%20vision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20occasionally%20took%20aim%20at%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20richest%