target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewmax's%20stock%20debut%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20the%20talk%20of%20Wall%20Street%2C%20but%20the%20investment%20bank%20behind%20the%20deal%20is%20not%20normally%20associated%20with%20the%20sector's%20splashiest%20IPOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20using%20a%20large%20advisory%20firm%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-investment-bank-leaders-lay-out-winning-strategy-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGoldman%2520Sachs%2527%2520core%2520business%2520of%2Cinclude%2520making%2520teams%2520more%2520specialized.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsmax-stock-price-soars-latest-meme-nmax-post-ipo-boom-2025-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNewsmax%2520has%2520cemented%2520its%2520status%2Can%2520intraday%2520high%2520of%2520%2524229.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsmax%3C%2Fa%3E%20tapped%20a%20relatively%20obscure%20advisor%3A%20Laguna%20Beach%2C%20California-based%20Digital%20Offering%20LLC%2C%20which%20has%20just%20six%20full-time%20registered%20bankers.%20The%20stock%20debut%20has%20helped%20put%20the%20bank%20on%20the%20map%20and%20is%20already%20driving%20new%20business%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20said%20Mark%20Elenowitz%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20based%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20huge%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Elenowitz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20small-cap%20community%20knows%20who%20we%20are%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20Wall%20Street%20didn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Offering%20advises%20companies%20valued%20at%20%241%20billion%20or%20less%20%E2%80%94%20what's%20considered%20small%20potatoes%20for%20some%20bulge-bracket%20shops.%20The%20bank%20also%20specializes%20in%20the%20unconventional%20method%20Newsmax%20used%20to%20sell%20its%20stock%20to%20the%20public%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20hire%20a%20bunch%20of%20banks%20to%20underwrite%20the%20IPO%20and%20sell%20the%20stocks%20to%20large%20investors%20in%20a%20roadshow%2C%20Newsmax%20relied%20on%20a%20lower-cost%2C%20less%20onerous%20form%20of%20a%20public%20offering%20termed%20Regulation%20A%2B%2C%20a%20provision%20of%20the%20Jumpstart%20Our%20Business%20Startups%20Act%2C%20which%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20signed%20into%20law%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative%20news%20station%20raised%20%2475%20million%20selling%207.5%20million%20shares%20at%20%2410%20each%20through%20this%20process%2C%20sometimes%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bmini%20IPO.%26quot%3B%20Despite%20Newsmax%20losing%20%2472%20million%20in%202024%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsmax-stock-price-soars-650-ipo-debut-trump-news-frenzy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20shot%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20735%25%20on%20its%20first%20day%20of%20trading%20and%20another%20180%25%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20close%20up%20over%201%2C200%25%20for%20the%20week%20at%20%24233.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20for%20this%20type%20of%20offering%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-mergers-acquisitions-ipos-hiring-slumps-trump-tariffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20firms%20like%20Digital%20Offering.%20Elenowitz%20said%20some%20mid-cap%20investment%20bank%20advisory%20firms%20have%20already%20reached%20out%20in%20recent%20days%20to%20express%20their%20desire%20to%20partner%20on%20public%20offerings%20structured%20similarly%20to%20Newsmax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20us%20to%20help%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20this%20type%20of%20stock%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d8eff9a-9a3c-4d32-83c7-d6ee81977948%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20with%20Newsmax%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20relationship%20with%20Newsmax%20began%20in%20August%202023%2C%20Elenowitz%20recounted.%20At%20first%2C%20Digital%20Offering%20helped%20Newsmax%20raise%20%24225%20million%20in%20capital%20from%20accredited%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsmax%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20the%20Regulation%20A%2B%20method%20for%20taking%20a%20company%20public%2C%20and%20Digital%20Offering%20was%20able%20to%20enumerate%20its%20vision.%20%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20that%20it%20would%20really%20create%20visibility%20for%20the%20company%20beyond%20just%20raising%20money%2C%20but%20actually%20creating%20visibility%20for%20the%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElenowitz%20spearheaded%20the%20Newsmax%20transaction%20alongside%20Gordon%20McBean%2C%20the%20bank's%20cofounder%20and%20chairman%20and%20a%20veteran%20of%20Lehman%20Brothers%20and%20Wells%20Fargo%3B%20and%20Mike%20Boswell%2C%20an%20MD%20who%20also%20has%20business%20interests%20in%20the%20defense%20sector%20and%20blockchain%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Offering%20saw%20Newsmax%20as%20the%20right%20candidate%20for%20a%20Regulation%20A%2B%20offering%20because%20of%20its%20consumer%20appeal.%20Whereas%20a%20traditional%20IPO%20prioritizes%20large%20institutional%20investors%2C%20a%20Reg%20A%20offering%20lets%20companies%20raise%20money%20from%20accredited%20and%20non-accredited%20investors%2C%20including%20mom-and-pop%20retail%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20buying%2C%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20a%20million%20dollars%20and%20really%20being%20concerned%2C%20these%20are%20investors%20that%20are%20buying%20%24500%2C%20%241000%26quot%3B%20worth%20of%20equity%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20gives%20management%20the%20time%20to%20stop%20worrying%20about%20their%20stock%20price%20and%20focus%20on%20growth%20their%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20past%2048%20hours%20have%20been%20a%20rush%20for%20Elenowitz.%20The%20phones%20have%20been%20ringing%20off%20the%20hook%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20rejoiced%20over%20a%20celebratory%