%20to%20him%20with%20a%20revised%20bail%20package%20and%20new%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20up%20with%20a%20package%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20advised%2C%20after%20suggesting%20he%20would%20consider%20ditching%20the%20ankle%20monitor%20if%20some%20other%20constraints%20%E2%80%94%20including%20an%20electronically%20monitored%20home%20curfew%20%E2%80%94%20were%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20come%20up%20with%20a%20successful%20package%20you%20would%20be%20able%20to%20change%20the%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%2033%2C%20teaches%20Pilates%20in%20Miami%20Beach%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20live%20in%20the%20same%20waterfront%20apartment%20building.%20In%20her%20previous%20career%2C%20she%20founded%20Frank%2C%20a%20website%20that%20helped%20students%20fill%20out%20their%20federal%20financial%20aid%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20found%20on%20Friday%20that%20Javice%20used%20fake%20data%20to%20trick%20JPMorgan%2C%20the%20country's%20largest%20bank%2C%20into%20believing%20her%20website%20had%20gathered%20the%20names%20and%20other%20personal%20data%20of%20more%20than%204%20million%20students.%20The%20bank%20had%20hoped%20to%20market%20checking%20accounts%20and%20credit%20cards%20to%20these%20students%2C%20but%20later%20found%20that%20Javice%20had%20data%20for%20fewer%20than%20300%2C000%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20ankle%20monitor%20decision%20on%20Tuesday%20followed%20some%2090%20minutes%20of%20arguments%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20with%20court%20exhibits%20showing%20Javice%20teaching%20Pilates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20arguing%20against%20the%20ankle%20monitor%2C%20Javice's%20lawyer%2C%20Ron%20Sullivan%2C%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20Javice%20has%20never%20missed%20a%20day%20of%20court%20and%20is%20not%20a%20flight%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20the%20bulky%20device%20once%20again%20%E2%80%94%20as%20she%20had%20for%20several%20weeks%20before%20a%20November%20decision%20granting%20its%20removal%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20a%20severe%20impediment%20to%20her%20career%20as%20a%20Pilates%20instructor%2C%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20have%20your%20legs%20in%20the%20air%20and%20the%20monitor%20going%20up%20and%20down%20on%20your%20leg%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20a%20significant%20encumbrance%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20told%20the%20judge.%20The%20lawyer%20held%20both%20arms%20aloft%20and%20waved%20them%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20demonstrate%20as%20he%20stood%20at%20a%20podium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20wearing%20an%20ankle%20bracelet%20previously%2C%20she%20was%20only%20able%20to%20teach%20lessons%20briefly%2C%20and%20for%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20classes%20require%20%26quot%3Bdemanding%20physical%20movement%20and%20full%20flexibility%20and%20range%20of%20motion%2C%20specifically%20around%20her%20feet%20and%20ankles%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20lawyers%20argued%20in%20court%20filings%20earlier%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Javice's%20services%20are%20sought%20after%20because%20her%20instruction%20is%20particularly%20challenging%20and%20dynamic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hellerstein's%20courtroom%2C%20an%20assistant%20US%20attorney%20countered%20that%20an%20ankle%20bracelet%20is%20necessary%20now%20that%20Javice%2C%20who%20holds%20dual%20French-US%20citizenship%2C%20has%20been%20convicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20be%20well%20within%20our%20rights%20to%20seek%20remand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20prosecutor%2C%20Georgia%20V.%20Kostopoulos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20understand%20that%20pretrial%20services%20would%20not%20be%20opposed%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20agency%20that%20handles%20post-conviction%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance%20does%20not%20have%20an%20extradition%20agreement%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20prosecutors%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHellerst