%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20does%20not%20fit%20the%20profile%20of%20a%20death%20penalty%20eligible%20criminal%2C%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20Tuesday%20after%20Attorney%20General%20Pam%20Bondi%20said%20the%20government%20would%20seek%20the%20ultimate%20penalty%20in%20what%20she%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bcold-blooded%20assassination%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangione-pam-bondi-death-penalty-murder-case-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20in%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20Savitt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20a%20mass%20shooting.%20It's%20not%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20It's%20a%20horrible%20crime%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20as%20serious%20as%20it%20is%2C%20it%20does%20not%20fit%20in%20the%20rubric%20of%20someone%20who%20should%20be%20put%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMangione%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20sentenced%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20is%20facing%20charges%20in%20three%20jurisdictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20least%20serious%20are%20the%20weapons%20and%20forgery%20charges%20out%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20the%2026-year-old%20software%20developer%20from%20Maryland%20was%20arrested%20after%20a%20five-day%20manhunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20facing%20state-level%20charges%20of%20murder%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terror%20out%20of%20Manhattan%2C%20where%20District%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg%20has%20said%20Mangione%20will%20be%20tried%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione's%20federal%20jury%20would%20be%20chosen%20from%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20which%20includes%20people%20from%20Manhattan%2C%20the%20Bronx%2C%20Westchester%20County%2C%20and%20five%20other%20counties%20on%20the%20southern%20end%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20federal%20court%2C%20now%20that%20this%20is%20an%20official%20death%20penalty%20case%2C%20a%20single%20trial%20jury%20would%20preside%20over%20a%20phase%20to%20determine%20Mangione's%20guilt%20and%20then%20another%20to%20determine%20how%20he%20should%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de315f31-7338-44a5-92c5-d5e250ede040%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20strategy%20in%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20would%20consist%20only%20of%20people%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20impose%20a%20death%20penalty%2C%20tilting%20it%20in%20the%20government's%20favor%2C%20Savitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20improves%20your%20odds%20of%20a%20conviction%2C%20absolutely%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Savitt%2C%20of%20the%20Ephraim%20Savitt%20Law%20Firm%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20two%20key%20strategic%20benefits%20to%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20former%20prosecutors%20said%2C%20even%20if%20an%20ultimate%20verdict%20of%20death%20may%20be%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20strategic%20benefit%20to%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%20is%20it%20gives%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20leverage%26quot%3B%20in%20plea%20negotiations%2C%20said%20another%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%2C%20Michael%20Bachner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20the%20defense%20lawyer%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20work%20it%20out%20as%20a%20package%20%E2%80%94%20he%20pleads%20to%20both%20cases%20and%20there's%20no%20death%20penalty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bachner%2C%20now%20in%20private%20practice%20at%20Bachner%20%26amp%3B%20Associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Mangione's%20favor%20is%20that%20a%20death%20penalty%20verdict%20must%20be%20unanimous.%20The%20defense%20needs%20to%20convince%20only%20one%20juror%20that%20Mangione%20does%20not%20deserve%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20Bachner%20and%20Saviott%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20former%20prosecutors%20said%2C%20strategy%20aside%2C%20the%20real%20benefit%20to%20seeking%20the%20death%20penalty%20was%20political.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20count%20against%20Mangione%20%E2%80%94%20murder%20t