repreneurship-1743071955-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FInclusive-entrepreneurship-1743071955-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416308%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnita%20Mourya%20in%20her%20sari%20production%20unit.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Anita%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20income%20has%20doubled%2C%20and%20her%20business%20is%20thriving.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20financially%20empowered%20and%20confident%20about%20securing%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20evidence%20of%20how%20innovation%2C%20when%20paired%20with%20opportunity%20and%20support%2C%20can%20transform%20lives.%20From%20a%20factory%20worker%20to%20a%20business%20leader%2C%20her%20journey%20is%20one%20of%20resilience%20and%20creativity%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20others%20in%20her%20community.%C2%A0%20Anita%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20expanding%20the%20online%20presence%20of%20her%20business%20and%20creating%20more%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20job%20seekers%20to%20job%20creators%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Development%20Alternatives%E2%80%99%20Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%20Programme%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20set%20up%20of%2026000%2B%20enterprises%20creating%2040000%20jobs%20across%20478%20villages%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mirzapur%2C%20Bahraich%2C%20Niwari%2C%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Lakhimpur%2C%20and%20the%20Bundelkhand%20region%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%3F%2056%25%20of%20these%20jobs%20are%20women-led.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20led%20to%20a%2065%20percent%20increase%20in%20annual%20revenue%20for%20entrepreneurs%20associated%20with%20it.%20For%20Anita%2